main event: A report from Project Blue Book documenting a sighting of rapidly moving objects evaluated as probably meteors in Sweden on 17 May 1954.
interesting points: The sighting was reported by a general (ret.) without a copy of the original report., The analysis concluded the objects were astronomical phenomena., The observation was made visually from the ground., The report is linked to CIA ATIC documentation., The objects were observed recently prior to the report date of 27 July 1954.
